{{cite book | title = Illustrated Glossary of Packaging Terms | author = Soroka, W | publisher = Institute of Packaging Professionals | year = 2008 | isbn = 1-930268-27-0 | page = 33 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | title = Corrugated Crossroads | author = Koning, J | publisher = TAPPI Press | year = 1995 | isbn = 0-89852-299-4 | page =35 }}</ref><ref name="李广才 2011">{{Cite journal
